DBpedia,is,a,web,tool,built,to,extract,structured,information,from,Wikipedia,convert,it,into,RDF,and,make,it,freely,available,on,the,Web,In,a,nutshell,DBpedia,is,the,Semantic,Web,mirror,of,Wikipedia,The,DBpedia,Spotlight,API,is,a,RESTful,API,tool,for,annotating,mentions,of,DBpedia,resources,in,text,providing,a,solution,for,linking,unstructured,information,sources,to,the,Linked,Open,Data,cloud,DBpedia,Spotlight,performs,named,entity,extraction,including,entity,detection,and,Name,Resolution,At,this,time,the,DBpedia,Spotlight,API,is,free,and,requires,no,sign,up,or,registration,to,use